archetypes.title: The Mystic Thinker
archetypes.description: You relate to life through the pressure of 'Knowing.' You often hear the truth before you see it, finding yourself preoccupied with deep mysteries and sudden awareness.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry an undercurrent of sudden insight and mental pressure that drives you toward the unknown.

archetypes.title: The Innovative Genius
archetypes.description: Your lived experience is one of breakthroughs. You take complex, 'weird' ideas and structure them into concepts that can change the future path for others.
archetypes.secondary_description: You have a secondary ability to simplify the complex and initiate others through your unique insights.

archetypes.title: The System Corrector
archetypes.description: You relate to the world by seeing what is broken. You feel a deep pressure to challenge current patterns and perfect them for the collective joy of life.
archetypes.secondary_description: You bring a secondary drive for logic and detail that ensures long-term viability.

archetypes.title: The Nurturing Guardian
archetypes.description: Your experience is centered on the health of your 'tribe.' You relate to others through an instinctive responsibility to protect, nourish, and care for the spirit.
archetypes.secondary_description: You possess a secondary protective instinct that creates a sense of safety and community.

archetypes.title: The Resource Leader
archetypes.description: You relate to others through the management of life's material resources. You ensure the tribe is fed, clothed, and fairly organized for survival.
archetypes.secondary_description: You have a secondary talent for bargaining and maintaining the physical infrastructure of your groups.

archetypes.title: The Creative Pulse
archetypes.description: You live a life of unique, rhythmic expression. Your inner pulse acts as a beacon of inspiration for those who have lost their own creative direction.
archetypes.secondary_description: You bring an independent streak that encourages others to follow their own unique inner timing.

archetypes.title: The Ambitious Achiever
archetypes.description: Your lived experience is a climb toward success. You show others what is possible when raw ambition is paired with instinctive endurance.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry a secondary drive for transformation and material success that others find grounding.

archetypes.title: The Sensitive Synthesizer
archetypes.description: You relate to others through emotional sensitivity. You feel the needs of the community and seek to create synthesis and spiritual abundance.
archetypes.secondary_description: You possess a secondary ability to sense the spiritual needs of your tribe and bridge those gaps.

archetypes.title: The Passionate Adventurer
archetypes.description: Your life is a series of emotional cycles that lead to wisdom. You share your experiences of desire and trial-and-error to help the collective grow.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry an intense undercurrent of experience that sparks movement and reflection in others.

archetypes.title: The Focused Master
archetypes.description: You live in a world of deep concentration and skill. You stay still until a logical pattern is fully understood or a cycle is perfectly finished.
archetypes.secondary_description: You bring a secondary stillness and disciplined focus that allows for high-level mastery.

archetypes.title: The Instinctive Entrepreneur
archetypes.description: You relate to others through your 'nose' for opportunity. You use instinctive memory to sell ideas and products that thrive in the now.
archetypes.secondary_description: You possess a secondary survival instinct that ensures you stay competitive and relevant.

archetypes.title: The Shock Catalyst
archetypes.description: Your presence is initiatory. You relate to others by 'shocking' them into a new way of being, taking leaps into the unknown with competitive power.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry a secondary frequency of pure mutation and mutation that disrupts the status quo.

archetypes.title: The Community Negotiator
archetypes.description: You relate to others through the heart. You understand that community is built on loyalty, fair deals, and physical bonding.
archetypes.secondary_description: You have a secondary drive for spiritualizing tribal agreements and maintaining communal peace.

archetypes.title: The Experimental Sage
archetypes.description: Your lived experience is one of 'trial and error.' You dive into cycles of experience and share the wisdom of your journey when the dust settles.
archetypes.secondary_description: You possess a secondary ability to abstract meaning from the past and turn it into stories.

archetypes.title: The Rhythmic Guide
archetypes.description: You live in flow with the natural patterns of life. Your internal clock draws others into a healthy, productive, and stable rhythm.
archetypes.secondary_description: You bring a secondary stability to environments by aligning with the natural flow of time.

archetypes.title: The Charismatic Manifestor
archetypes.description: You relate to the world through pure, busy activity. Your energy is infectious, turning your convictions into busy reality in the blink of an eye.
archetypes.secondary_description: You carry a secondary frequency of power and self-direction that others find magnetic and unstoppable.
